data.description: Located in the heart of the popular South of Broadway neighborhood. There is no shortage of activities. From the sprawling convention center, live music venues, and top-rated restaurants this up and coming area will have you feeling like a local right away. The home is located within a safe fenced in yard with a 2-car detached garage. Once walking into the home you will notice the hardwood floors throughout, plenty of natural light and the inviting French doors. The unique personality shows throughout with three spacious bedrooms and a master suite, and a large kitchen that has an abundance of storage space and great character.  Both the den and the attic can be converted to a bedroom or living space. This home has everything a buyer could want and then some.
